Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在正被逼至绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，他却在享受这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打从内心，兴奋的期待着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9局下半，两出局满垒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙现在脑里只想着\n要把球打出场外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛毒(Venom)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙现在正朝着球场走去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊爆危机\N FULL METAL PANlC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#24 lNTO THE BLUE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真高兴啊，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九龙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C3系统第11号电源线被切断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从C4转接过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力丧失20%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库C区探测到火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2气密门的内壁破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰内温度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库防火隔间无法关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用手动关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁在那附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第7、8、9蓄水池破损
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注40的水进第10至15蓄水池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急排出所有的喷射燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左舷第2、第3ECS杆损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来把那个粗暴的家伙\n给我赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没辄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你赢了，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不，好像也不是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动SDM，120秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告，启动后无法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您同意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，快点动手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会陪我到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算自我引爆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来当好朋友吧，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舱门？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧，还剩60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附带一提，炸药有300公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,份量足以炸沉这艘船舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，你要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是巴萨狄那的主动鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从方位2-9-8接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好诱饵机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快准备再度潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高压空气尚未充填完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离2500
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认鱼雷发射管口的开启声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说想跟你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阁…阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊，不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除所有攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就等于是终于得到了\n期望已久的初次打击机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛却因太阳西下而告中止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼雷没来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是跟丢了我方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴萨狄那，在距离1500处停止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行舱门正在开启
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种暴风雨中\n打开飞行舱门根本是自杀行为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann没有任何异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令是从别处发出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(不用担心，一切都会很顺利)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的，不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样？这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得很难看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你像英雄那般\n帅气的将我一次击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死命挣扎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起华丽又滑稽的走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办？甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只剩15秒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认全舰的空气密闭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以关闭飞行舱门为优先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小要，强弩兵(Arbalest)呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么亲密地叫我\n卡西姆、卡西姆的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他骂狗屎家伙耶，大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，我说了一些没大脑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的事还一点都不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的觉得你很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜航，潜航，潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,53、54、55节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深度500，锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人尾随
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Danann，剩下就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的，千鸟小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理查德·马德加斯中校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉·葛达特上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波布·莱利中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史裘瓦特·亚凯尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·马卡兰上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了，长官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深感光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马卡兰上尉正在巡逻中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅莉莎·毛上士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁兹·威巴中士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介中士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梁小平一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在巡逻中，舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经在那边站10分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介，你去跟她说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫她打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟我一起来吗？千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会做奇怪的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危险吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里，千鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说那个，这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的钓场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地里只有我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.02,0:19:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要搭往东京的班机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能在这里\n再待40多分钟而已耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.26,0:19:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我当被的作战目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就是想带你来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却因为各种事而绕了一大圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到…到这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来，钓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定30分钟就可以钓到大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋，怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就很难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是钓上超乎想像的大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是从恐怖的危险中逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30分钟就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微陪我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么觉得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有你在，我现在才能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就来试试\n你所说的这种好运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拉了，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲷鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是鲸鱼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不能否定这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要把它钓回家去喔，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人一起寻找逃避之处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太阳雨中奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有一件事 一定要去保护
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生于这个世界的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起去寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使拥抱着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去迎接新的景色
